">Brandes, Georg</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02281">Adam an Schnitzler, 23. 11. 1917</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02283">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 12. 4. 1918</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02274">Brandes an Schnitzler, 28. 9. 1917</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02292">Schnitzler an Brandes, 2. 8. 1918</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
